(4, '2008-09-30 01:09:25', '\r\n<div class="commonbox">\r\n  <div class="cmnbx_title"><h1>Privacy Policy </h1>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="cmnbx_box_body"><span>\r\n      <table height="22" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%" align="center" border="0">\r\n        <tbody>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top"><strong>We greet you on your very first visit to indian foods online.</strong></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">An easier way to book or order online. </td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">At <a href="/?phpMyAdmin=f8f18aff8034c7fc010b4323190c5fc3">www.indianfoodsonline.co.uk</a>, we make a solemn vow to safeguard the confidentiality of our guests and visitors. Which is why, we would like you to peruse through the following privacy policy, as it gives a detailed description of the manner in which we utilise your personal facts and consequently guard them.</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">According to the stipulations of our privacy policy, you automatically agree to the employment, compilation, and transmission of your personal data once you visit the website or place an order for a service. </td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top"><strong>PERSONAL FACTS YOU DISCLOSE ON OUR WEBSITE </strong></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">As is customary, you are asked to provide information like your name, phone number, home address as well as your email address when you visit ‘indian foods online’ or place an order on the website. Your communication on/with the website – posts, messages and emails – also provide us with more information about you. Nevertheless, your monetary information that includes details about your credit or debit cards is not held on our server till you request or purchase a service. We must mention here that this information is taken on a protected page and is later discarded as soon as your payment is received. This is our standard procedure and you will be alerted in case of any change. </td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top"><strong>HOW WE EMPLOY YOUR PERSONAL DATA </strong></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">When you give us your personal details, it helps us direct you to pertinent areas of the website that hold your interest as well as offer you related services. Besides, getting in touch with you becomes much simpler as does billing you for services rendered. An important function of collating this information lies in our constant endeavour to better the services offered on our website, so as to expand our company. If you are agreeable to our website contacting you for your views on our services, we may do so by sending you an SMS, an email or may even call you. This communication can also include news about new products and services that we may have started on the website. In case of you not wanting to be contacted, you can inform us of the same.</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top"><strong>DIVULGING YOUR PERSONAL DATA </strong></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\