ll only restrict you from using all the features of the website. </td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top"><strong>SECURING AND PRESERVING YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION </strong></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">Your personal data is kept on our website safely for only as long as required. We ensure that no illegal sources are able to obtain your information through unlawful means and then use it for their own advantage. </td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top"><strong>KEEPING THE WEBSITE UP-TO-DATE</strong></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">You only have to get in touch with us if you wish to access your personal information on the website and update it for precise dealings in the future.</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody>\r\n      </table></span>\r\n    <div class="cmnbx_footer"><h1></h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>', 'Privacy Policy', 'Publish', '2009-07-08 22:07:11', 0, 2, '<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1" />\r\n<title>Just Eat and Relax while you have Indian foods online| UK''s leading online indian takeaway and delivery food ordering provider</title>\r\n\r\n<meta name="author" content="Indian Foods Online" />\r\n<meta http-equiv="expires" content="NEVER" />\r\n<meta name="publisher" content="Indian Foods Online" />\r\n<meta name="copyright" content="Indian Foods Online" />\r\n<meta name="page-topic" content="Restaurants" />\r\n<meta name="keywords" content="order indian foods online, indian takeaway, online currys, online table booking, tikka, ma