(80, 93, 10, 7, 'Moksh Divine Indian Cuisine', 'Ocean Buildings Bute Crescent', 'Cardiff', 'CF10 5AY', 'United Kingdom', '0292 049 8120', '', '', '', 'http://indianfoodsonline.co.uk/index-action-restaurant_details_view-rid-80', '', '', '\r\n<table width="100%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2" border="0">\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="myriad15"><strong>Food for thought</strong></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">"One of the very nicest things about life is the way we must regularly stop whatever it is we aredoing and\r\ndevote our attention to eating."</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td class="myriad15_gray">\r\n        <div align="right">-Luciano Pavaroti\r\n        </div></td>\r\n      <td class="arial12">&nbsp;</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="myriad15"><strong>Chef Stephen comments: </strong></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">On a culinary  level we have made  our very sincere  efforts to keep the authenticity of the food true to its\r\n        <br />original recipes.We have used the best  herbs and spices to give a natural  aroma of Indian food.</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="tb_h">\r\n        <br /></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="myriad15"><strong>Our Achievements</strong></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">Cardiff City Council Food Hygiene Awards 2007/08\r\n        <br />                      Stephen Gomes - Chef of the Year 2006/07\r\n        <br />                      Craft Guild of Chefs 2006/07\r\n        <br />                      Master Chef Roll of Honour 2003</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="tb_h">\r\n        <br /></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="myriad15"><strong>The Famous Food Critics Verdict</strong></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">We are already discussing a return visit before we have finished the obligatory naan mop-up. </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td class="arial12">\r\n        <div align="right"><strong>- Red Handed</strong>\r\n        </div></td>\r\n      <td class="myriad15_gray">&nbsp;</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">Moksh has aspirations that go beyond a traditional curry house.</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td class="arial12">\r\n        <div align="right"><strong>- Metro</strong>\r\n        </div></td>\r\n      <td class="myriad15_gray">&nbsp;</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">1 am one of the few people in the country who doesn''t like Indian food (there I''ve said it!) but\r\n        <br />a visit to Moksh has set me on the road to conversion. </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td class="arial12">\r\n        <div align="right"><strong>- Cathy Owen / Echo</strong>\r\n        </div></td>\r\n      <td class="myriad15_gray">&nbsp;</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">A visit to Moksh is throughly enjoyable and satisfying experience.</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td class="arial12">\r\n        <div align="right"><strong>- Antonio Levay</strong>\r\n        </div></td>\r\n      <td class="myriad15_gray">&nbsp;</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">Moksh aims to cater for those who love their curry, but also love chic and stylish surroundings.</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td class="arial12">\r\n        <div align="right"><strong>- Ladies First</strong>\r\n        </div></td>\r\n      <td class="myriad15_gray">&nbsp;</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan="2" class="arial12">Fine dining Indian cuisine without the price tag. Stylish, sophisticated, delicious - what more \r\n        <br />                      could you want? </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="88%